snippet.title: SWORD ART ONLINE Last Recollection — Original Characters Trailer
snippet.description:
Fates that have crossed intertwine again as original characters from 10 years of SWORD ART ONLINE games unite to fight once more!

SWORD ART ONLINE Last Recollection launches on PlayStation 4|5, Xbox One and Xbox Series X|S, and Steam on October 6, 2023!
Pre-orders are available now: https://www.bandainamcoent.com/games/sword-art-online-last-recollection
Every Digital Pre-order includes a weapon skin set pre-order bonus featuring iconic weapons from the SWORD ART ONLINE series!

#SWORDARTONLINE #LASTRECOLLECTION
